      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Pierce the Heavens",
        "Client": "Admiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Reports are coming in of a\r\nRajang variant in the Frost\r\nIslands. Its savagery knows\r\nno bounds, and if left unchecked,\r\nwe are sure to have a crisis on\r\nour hands. ...Hunter, will you\r\nlend us your strength?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Furious Rajang",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Rupture c\u00E9leste",
        "Client": "Amiral Galleus",
        "Description": "Une esp\u00E8ce unique de Rajang\r\na apparemment \u00E9t\u00E9 signal\u00E9e\r\ndans l\u0027Archipel de glace. Leur\r\nsauvagerie n\u0027a aucune limite,\r\ntout comme les d\u00E9g\u00E2ts qu\u0027ils\r\npeuvent causer... Je compte\r\nsur toi pour nous aider.",
